What the heck are you screaming about?

43
00:03:53,839 --> 00:03:55,292
It's just a little bump on your head.

44
00:03:55,567 --> 00:03:57,791
I've seen you fall out of a tree
and almost break your leg,

45
00:03:58,222 --> 00:03:59,928
and you didn't make this much fuss.

46
00:04:00,591 --> 00:04:01,611
- P'Parik!
- Ouch!

47
00:04:01,918 --> 00:04:04,608
Come on! She's your daughter,
for heaven’s sake!

48
00:04:05,221 --> 00:04:08,850
Loy bullied her like this,
and you're still yelling at her?

49
00:04:08,913 --> 00:04:12,191
If it were you who got hurt,
I wouldn't say a word.

50
00:04:12,238 --> 00:04:13,964
Oh, come on, Lamphoei.

51
00:04:14,140 --> 00:04:17,174
They were just playing a little rough,
what's the big deal?

52
00:04:17,631 --> 00:04:20,130
