does it hurt a lot, honey?

55
00:04:27,751 --> 00:04:29,784
You're crying your eyes out!

56
00:04:30,416 --> 00:04:33,408
I'm not crying because I'm in pain, Mom.

57
00:04:33,409 --> 00:04:36,090
I'm crying because
I feel sorry for P'Loy.

58
00:04:36,447 --> 00:04:37,823
Oh, P'Kaew.

59
00:04:37,923 --> 00:04:41,790
What the heck possessed you to do that to P'Loy?

60
00:04:42,185 --> 00:04:45,007
Oh, Whan, look at your own brother!

61
00:04:45,327 --> 00:04:48,163
Your own brother's hurt,
and you're taking that guy's side?

62
00:04:50,710 --> 00:04:53,757
- Bua, let's go see P'Loy.
- Absolutely not!

63
00:04:55,266 --> 00:04:56,281
Sit down!

64
00:04:56,653 --> 00:04:59,055
You're not running off to see any guys anymore.

65
00:04:59,137 --> 00:05:03,069
From now on, you're not going to be
hanging around any of those boatmen.

66
00:05:03,226 --> 00:05:04,464
Especially Loy.

67
00:05:04,721 --> 00:05:07,433
Why can't I, Mom?!

68
00:05:07,765 --> 00:05:09,131
No means no. That’s final!

69
00:05:09,370 --> 00:05:14,196
This dry season, Kamnan Boonlue is coming to
ask for your hand in marriage for Phaad.

70
00:05:14,297 --> 00:05:17,575
If you go around acting all loose,
it won't look good.

71
00:05:18,019 --> 00:05:23,446
Oh, Mom! That filthy bastard Phaad?
I wouldn't waste myself on garbage like him!

72
00:05:23,803 --> 00:05:26,008
Oh! This daughter of mine!

73
00:05:26,215 --> 00:05:29,040
Whan! My brother, my brother!

74
00:05:29,516 --> 00:05:32,274
Watch your mouth!
If you curse him again, I'll...

75
00:05:32,356 --> 00:05:34,946
Ow! It hurts... it hurts!

76
00:05:38,613 --> 00:05:39,638
P'Kaew.

77
00:05:39,883 --> 00:05:43,698
