81
00:05:57,894 --> 00:06:00,499
- Whan!
- Whan! / - Whan!

82
00:06:00,500 --> 00:06:02,104
- Whan!
- Whan!

83
00:06:02,411 --> 00:06:05,783
Calm down, okay?
Let's just talk this out slowly.

84
00:06:05,809 --> 00:06:09,572
If you keep this up,
Aunt Lamphoei will have my head for sure.

85
00:06:09,935 --> 00:06:11,912
True! Calm down first.

86
00:06:15,378 --> 00:06:18,102
