- Whan!

95
00:06:36,958 --> 00:06:40,224
- I swear, I'm gonna smash your head in today!
- Whan!

96
00:06:40,481 --> 00:06:42,257
- Let go of me! Ow! Let me go!
- Whan!

97
00:06:42,258 --> 00:06:43,640
