113
00:07:47,804 --> 00:07:50,769
Ugh, there's so many leaves.
Does she ever sweep?

114
00:07:50,770 --> 00:07:52,602
- Why don't you go help her sweep?
- Are you kidding?

115
00:07:52,603 --> 00:07:55,093
- Well, you were complaining.
- But there really are a lot.

116
00:07:56,751 --> 00:07:58,295
I know about this because...

117
00:07:58,389 --> 00:08:03,907
