why don't you go live with him?

136
00:09:20,645 --> 00:09:21,653
Well...

137
00:09:21,691 --> 00:09:25,801
Well, well, Whan,
the beautiful girl of Thung Bang Maklua,

138
00:09:26,121 --> 00:09:28,323
that all the young men desire

139
00:09:28,711 --> 00:09:31,839
